# =============================================================================
# Gas City runtime state
# =============================================================================
# The .gc/ directory holds runtime state that regenerates on every city
# start or `gc init`:
#   - Per-agent session IDs, prompt tmp files, claude settings
#   - Controller/refinery/witness locks and PID files
#   - Unbounded event logs (events.jsonl)
#   - Nudge queue state
#   - Dolt runtime state (pid, lock, log, config)
#   - Generated system packs (.gc/system/*) — unpacked from the gc binary
#
# None of this is portable across machines. The context that matters lives
# outside .gc/: city.toml, packs/, formulas/, prompts/, .beads/metadata.json.
.gc/

# =============================================================================
# Beads / Dolt
# =============================================================================
# Dolt storage lives here when using local mode (non-server). The server-mode
# data directory is typically elsewhere and managed by the dolt pack.
.dolt/
*.db

# Beads local credentials (never commit secrets).
.beads-credential-key
